('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which action star has featured in both Terminator and Predator?', '["Sylvester Stallone","Jason Statham","Chuck Norris","Arnold Schwarzenegger"]', 3, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Name the movie that matches the following plot summary: ''A Hobbit and eight companions set out on a journey to destroy the powerful One Ring.''', '["The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring","Star Wars","Double Indemnity","Logan"]', 0, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which actor played the role of John McClane in Die Hard?', '["John Travolta","Bruce Willis","Sean Penn","Al Pacino"]', 1, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which of these quotes is from the film ''Dr. No''?', '["\"What we''ve got here is failure to communicate.\"","\"Sawyer, you''re going out a youngster, but you''ve t to come back a star!\"","\"Bond. James Bond.\"","\"Well, I don''t want to survive. I want to live.\""]', 2, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Name the movie that matches the following plot summary: ''Simba and his father are targeted by his uncle, who wants to ascend the throne himself.''', '["The Wizard of Oz","Joker","Rear Window","The Lion King"]', 3, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Who played the role of James Bond in Casino Royale?', '["Daniel Craig","George Lazenby","Roger Moore","Sean Connery"]', 0, 1),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'In 2009, which world leader was portrayed on-screen by Morgan Freeman?', '["Barack Obama","Nelson Mandela","Mahatma Gandhi","Winston Churchill"]', 1, 1),
