('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Name the movie that matches the following plot summary: ''The daughter of a plantation owner conducts a romance with a roguish profiteer.''', '["Downfall","Gone with the Wind","My Neighbour Totoro","Up"]', 1, 2),
