('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'What is the plot of the movie The Green Mile?', '["An archaeologist is hired by the government to find the Ark of the Covenant.","Two men searching for work in 1920s Mexico convince an old prospector to help them mine for gold.","The lives of guards on Death Row are affected by a man accused of child murder and rape.","After a mathematician accepts secret work in cryptography, his life takes a turn for the nightmarish."]', 2, 2),
