('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Name the movie that matches the following plot summary: ''A maverick teacher emboldens his students to new heights of self-expression.''', '["Dead Poets Society","Raging Bull","Modern Times","The Wizard of Oz"]', 0, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'What is the plot of the movie WALL·E?', '["On a journey to find the cure for a curse, a boy finds himself in the middle of a war.","In the future, a small waste-collecting robot inadvertently embarks on a space journey.","After a mathematician accepts secret work in cryptography, his life takes a turn for the nightmarish.","In a post-apocalyptic wasteland, a woman rebels against a tyrannical ruler."]', 1, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which actor played the role of Charles Foster Kane in Citizen Kane?', '["John Travolta","Bruce Willis","Orson Welles","Robert De Niro"]', 2, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which actor has appeared in films including No Country for Old Men and Skyfall?', '["Jason Bateman","Ken Jeong","Sean Penn","Javier Bardem"]', 3, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which actor played the role of Roger "Verbal" Kint in The Usual Suspects?', '["Kevin Spacey","Johnny Depp","Sean Penn","Samuel L. Jackson"]', 0, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'What is the plot of the movie Spirited Away?', '["An insane American general orders a bombing attack on the Soviet Union.","A girl wanders into a world ruled by gods, witches, and spirits, where humans are changed into beasts.","Held captive for 7 years, a woman and her young son finally gain their freedom.","A withdrawn boy who communicates with spirits seeks the help of a child psychologist."]', 1, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which of these quotes is from the film ''The Devil Wears Prada''?', '["\"I''ll be back.\"","\"Tell ''em to go out there with all they got and win just one for the Gipper.\"","\"I''m just one stomach flu away from my goal weight.\"","\"I''m the king of the world!\""]', 2, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'What is the plot of the movie The Father?', '["After awakening from a coma, a former assassin wreaks vengeance on those who betrayed her.","In World War II a group of soldiers go behind enemy lines to rescue a paratrooper.","An archaeologist is hired by the government to find the Ark of the Covenant.","A man refuses assistance as he ages and begins to his own mind."]', 3, 2),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which of these quotes is from the film ''Sons of the Desert''?', '["\"Well, here''s another nice mess you''ve gotten me into!\"","\"My precious.\"","\"After all, tomorrow is another day!\"","\"Gentlemen, you can''t fight in here! This is the War Room!\""]', 0, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'The role of Agent Peggy Carter in the Marvel Cinematic Universe is played by which actor?', '["Cobie Smulders","Hayley Atwell","Cate Blanchett","Evangeline Lilly"]', 1, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which of these quotes is from the film ''Moonstruck''?', '["\"I drink your milkshake. I drink it up.\"","\"Go ahead, make my day.\"","\"Snap out of it!\"","\"You''re gonna need a bigger boat.\""]', 2, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Name the movie that matches the following plot summary: ''A stranger joins forces with a desperado to protect a widow from an assassin.''', '["Mad Max: Fury Road","Shutter Island","The Good, the Bad and the Ugly","Once Upon a Time in the West"]', 3, 3),
