('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'In which year was Good Will Hunting released?', '["1989","1997","1993","2001"]', 1, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which actor is the father-in-law of Catherine Zeta-Jones?', '["Clint Eastwood","Burt Lancaster","Kirk Douglas","Anthony Hopkins"]', 2, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Who won the 2006 Academy Award for Best Leading Actress for playing the role of The Queen in The Queen?', '["Penélope Cruz","Judi Dench","Meryl Streep","Helen Mirren"]', 3, 3),
('c0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002', 'Which of these quotes is from the film ''On Golden Pond''?', '["\"Listen to me, mister. You''re my knight in shining armor. Don''t you forget it. You''re going to get back on that horse, and I''m going to be right behind you, holding on tight, and away we''re gonna , go, go!\"","\"What a dump.\"","\"What''s the most you ever lost on a coin toss?\"","\"Chewie, we''re home.\""]', 0, 3),
